Package com.vernalis.pdbconnector2

This package contains general utility classes for the new PDB Connector nodes

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HtmlEncoder
    This class provides a simple mechanism to HTML-escape and unescape named entity characters upto HTML 4
    InvalidSettingsExceptionCombiner
    A class to collect multiple InvalidSettingsExceptions during settings loading or validation, and throw a single InvalidSettingsException combining their message when InvalidSettingsExceptionCombiner.throwAll() is called
    PdbConnector2Helpers
    A helper class to generate a required query ID and to read the remote search metadata schema
    RcsbJSONConstants
    A class containing string contants required for parsing and creating JSON Queries and results
